## Links to Utilities

- [BleachBit](https://www.bleachbit.org/download/windows)
- [cCleaner Portable](https://www.ccleaner.com/ccleaner/builds)
- [PatchMyPC Home Updater](https://patchmypc.com/home-updater)
- [Revo Uninstaller Free](https://www.revouninstaller.com/start-freeware-download/)
- [Ninite Installer](https://ninite.com/) - [Essential Apps](https://ninite.com/7zip-firefox-irfanview-notepadplusplus-vlc/ninite.exe)
- [TeamViewer](https://download.teamviewer.com/download/TeamViewer_Setup_x64.exe)
- [Sysinternals Live](https://live.sysinternals.com/) / [Sysinternals Suite](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/downloads/sysinternals-suite)
- [CPU-ID](https://www.cpuid.com/softwares/cpu-z.html)

## Tasks

1. Windows Update - wuauclt.exe /updatenow 
2. Microsoft Office Update
3. Windows Store App Updates
4. Third-Party App Updates
5. Configure & Run Storage Sense
6. Check Autoruns - start run live.sysinternals.com/Autoruns64.exe
